title: Sniper Elite Nazi Zombie Army 2-FLT (2013) PC [MULTI6]
description:
============================================
Sniper Elite Nazi Zombie Army 2-FLT (2013) PC [MULTI6]
============================================

-  Languages: RUS, ENG,  Multi6 

============================================
Description:                               =
============================================

Experience a terrifyingly intense co-op campaign for up to four players in
 this gut-wrenching sequel to Steam best-seller, Sniper Elite: Nazi Zombie
 Army
 With World War 2 Europe overrun by legions of the undead, you must find
 mankind's salvation deep in the twisted bowels of Berlin by securing the
 sacred artefacts that unleashed this damnation. Every step must be paid in
 blood as players work together against impossible odds and descend further
 into the demon-infested city and the terrifying Fuehrerbunker itself   

============================================
Features:                                  =
============================================

* Survive an all new stand-alone campaign for up to four players
 * Endure increasingly hellish new locations and oppressive
 environments
 * Confront blood-chilling new enemies including the Fire Demon, and
 Summoner
 * Recoil at grotesque new enemies, effects and tense new
 cinematics
 * Savour the all-new Carpente         

============================================
Instruction:                               =
============================================

* Install
* Play
